<p>Bootstrap provides a handful of <a href="/arizona-bootstrap/docs/0.0/utilities/sizing/">utilities for setting width</a>. Depending on your needs, these may help with quickly configuring progress.</p>

<div class="bd-example">
<div class="progress">
  <div class="progress-bar w-75" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="75" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
</div>
</div>
